--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Urban Company Stocks Today, Urban Company IPO listing & share price live updates: Shares of Urban Company Ltd made their strong debut on the stock exchanges today, after running one of the most oversubscribed IPOs in recent times. The stock listed at ₹162.25 on the National Stock Exchange (NSE) and ₹161 on the BSE on September 17.
- Listing date and price: September 17. Lists at Rs 162.25 on the NSE and at Rs 161 on the BSE
- IPO: 1,900-cr IPO received 103.63 times subscription
The ₹1,900-crore IPO received 103.63 times subscription on the final day of bidding. The issue size comprised ₹472 crore through the sale of new shares and ₹1,428 crore from the sale of stakes by existing investors, with the price band set at ₹98-103. The anchor portion mobilised ₹854 crore.
Urban Company plans to utilize the funds raised through the fresh issuance for technology development and cloud infrastructure, lease payments for offices, marketing initiatives, and general corporate purposes. Investors can catch live updates on the IPO subscription, share price, listing price, GMP and more here.
